  "cscw_dialogue": [
    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要为后端微服务系统绘制一个用户旅程图，展示用户从登录到最终生成报告的完整流程。核心场景包括：身份认证、工时管理、费用管理、文档处理和报表查看这五个环节。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "User Journey for Backend Microservices",
        "Access",
        "Timesheet Management",
        "Expense Management",
        "Document Handling",
        "Reporting"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白了，五个section。我想确认一下评分标准——您希望用1到5的数字来表示用户满意度或流程顺畅度吗？比如登录环节相对简单给1分，最后的报表功能最复杂给5分？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "User logs in via Authentication",
        "User generates or views reports"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对的，就是这个意思。登录认证是基础入口，复杂度最低；工时提交和费用管理是日常高频操作，中等复杂度；文档上传下载涉及文件服务，稍微复杂些；最后的报表生成需要聚合多源数据，技术难度最高。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "User logs in via Authentication: 1",
        "User views or submits timesheet: 2",
        "User adds or reviews expenses: 3",
        "User uploads or downloads documents: 4",
        "User generates or views reports: 5"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我先搭建框架：标题定为\"User Journey for Backend Microservices\"，五个section依次是Access、Timesheet Management、Expense Management、Document Handling和Reporting。每个section下的具体任务描述我也按您说的写进去。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "title",
        "section Access",
        "section Timesheet Management",
        "section Expense Management",
        "section Document Handling",
        "section Reporting"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "等等，Document Handling那个环节，我想确认下表述——是写\"User uploads or downloads documents\"更准确，还是强调\"cuments\"相关的操作？另外Expense Management里用\"adds or reviews\"会不会比\"submits\"更贴切？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "User uploads or downloads documents",
        "User adds or reviews expenses"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "您的建议很好。Expense Management保持\"adds or reviews expenses\"，因为费用是新增和审核的概念；Document Handling用\"uploads or downloads\"更直观。Timesheet那边我用的\"views or submits\"，因为工时是先查看再提交，逻辑上区分开。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "User views or submits timesheet",
        "User adds or reviews expenses",
        "User uploads or downloads documents"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "完美。最后确认下Reporting环节——\"generates or views reports\"这个表述可以，但想强调这是旅程的终点，用户完成前面所有操作后才能到达这里。评分5分体现它的聚合性质。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "User generates or views reports: 5",
        "Reporting"
